COPA PRESIDENTE RUBENS HOFFMEISTER
Championship First Phase

Byes: (Clubs that disputed the Brazilian Championship 1978)
Internacional, Grêmio, Brasil, Juventude e Caxias
 
Copa Rubens Hoffmeister - Full Results
30 Jul
Final
Esportivo          3-1 Novo Hamburgo
 
Esportivo won Copa Pres. Rubens Hoffmeister and classified to Final Phase (Copa 60. Aniv. da FGF)
Novo Hamburgo, runner-up, and classified to Final Phase (Copa 60. Aniv. da FGF)
 
 
 
